title: "Coding discrete explanatory variables"
author: "Marc Dotson"
date: "2022-11-26"
description: |
  An exploration of the different ways to code discrete (i.e., categorical) explanatory variables and their equivalence via contrasts.
categories:
  - bayesian inference
  - stan
